          "trait_date": "2026-03-10T10:48:20.6241949+03:00",
          "locale_text": "«Parece que he arruinado tus planes. ¿Ahora qué?»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Ich scheine Eure Pläne durchkreuzt zu haben. Was jetzt?\"",
